songs.lyrics:

I'm knowing that you feel my sound
But you can only hear the lows
I'm crying now
You're flying out
I'm lying down

That's only if you know
Know me

It's only if you know me
Can your else see

Been doing dishes babe

[Breakdown]
songs.title: TnGwee #3
